data.revised_prompt: Create a high-resolution infographic that illustrates a polished product roadmap titled 'Social Media Marketing Dashboard — Epics & Delivery Timeline'. The layout should have a header titled 'Epics & Delivery Timeline (8 weeks)', a left column containing 6 epics as labeled blocks with brief bullets detailing their purpose and timeline, a right side showing a Gantt-style timeline indicating weeks 1–8 corresponding to the epics, and a footer box containing risks and mitigations. Use a clean, modern design aesthetic with a neutral background, high-contrast typography, and subtle iconography for each epic. Use brand-safe colors with accessible contrast and clear labels.
